{"tid":2498680,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（年經）返工做錯野最嚴重果次，累公司蝕左幾多錢？","createTime":"2021-04-21T10:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:19:01.000Z","uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9a448b4b980ed9aa7d0285a36a0acd8983f602","tid":2498680,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"試過喺一間物流公司做，負責幫貨船入油。果日有架船要出航遠行，咁我就一如往常咁打滿佢，送佢一程。過左一段時間就發現今次Hi Hi嘞，原來架船係用柴油嘅，點知一時錯手入左汽油。其實入錯油都冇咩，架船又唔會因為咁爆炸死人嘅；最多都係死火，啲貨就遲幾日到。不過公司就要賠錢，而我都有俾人炒嘅心理準備。當時都仲心存一絲希望，希望架船聽聽話話，捱到去終站。 <br />\n<br />\n不過架船真係喺太平洋島嶼擱淺左。我心諗出得嚟行，預左要還，已經準備定執包袱。果然好快就收到消息，不過炒嘅唔單止係我，而係成個部門十幾人，連上司嘅上司都俾人炒埋。點解呢？ 原來係架船上面係載住一啲化學物品，擱淺之後洩漏到成個海都係，公司要負責處理污染物，一賠賠幾億。而事件裡面最無辜嘅係附近一個水清沙幼嘅太平洋小島，因為生態災害，要即時封鎖隔離。 <br />\n<br />\n就因為遠在香港嘅我一時錯手，將一個太平洋小島毀於一旦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece84a0580e4537e320dd5f4422bc3aa7f5a3745","tid":2498680,"uid":124262,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"本來諗住入嚟睇潮文，估唔到樓主喺一樓已經post咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6576fe87d80094133ebee0a52957ba39c83f1e27","tid":2498680,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"1. 超速撞船塞運河<br />\n2. 工程車唔拉手掣炒火車"},{"pid":"30a6e34cfe01be602a0557611183ce613ba8c171","tid":2498680,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6576fe87d80094133ebee0a52957ba39c83f1e27","tid":2498680,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"1. 超速撞船塞運河<br />\n2. 工程車唔拉手掣炒火車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"蝕左幾錢？"},{"pid":"69c95d6816c93d39b30503fc373780101f8f9f6d","tid":2498680,"uid":227588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6576fe87d80094133ebee0a52957ba39c83f1e27","tid":2498680,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"1. 超速撞船塞運河<br />\n2. 工程車唔拉手掣炒火車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"一個人孭晒兩單？為咗人類存亡，一係去攞終援、一係做廢官嘅私人司機。"},{"pid":"ae71edcaf6d4fd6c0d83e502eeb3dde16852638e","tid":2498680,"uid":284038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"魚魚好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3a97965c2cc973119aecc263de7ceaa6ea8f4f","tid":2498680,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"長賜號係我揸旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206128cdf168017470a854ff3a4e753885ffab72","tid":2498680,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"燒錄錯左27隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為比人燒同人哋做光雕<br />\n最後賠左270蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68964acfb56b361c00ab4b701bc2c86cedb4edde","tid":2498680,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206128cdf168017470a854ff3a4e753885ffab72","tid":2498680,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"燒錄錯左27隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為比人燒同人哋做光雕<br />\n最後賠左270蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"公司有無破產"},{"pid":"e4e89d8e9f3196d284d30ee1f881eeb86d62b7da","tid":2498680,"uid":309520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"幫公司買license（3人用）<br />\n<br />\n比sells周，問我幾多人用<br />\n<br />\n我答&ldquo;唔知wo，成間公司都用緊掛&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到後食住上話要報警，我同佢講有咩事同我上司講<br />\n<br />\n最後冇事"},{"pid":"3e29b6256ef6208376a8a843e62df85799b11434","tid":2498680,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4e89d8e9f3196d284d30ee1f881eeb86d62b7da","tid":2498680,"uid":309520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-2